{
    "FR": {
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_NAME": "HUNK",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_DESCRIPTION": "HUNK est un infiltr\u00e9 d'\u00e9lite qui transporte un vaste arsenal d'armes obtenues via OSP (On-Site Procurement).<color=#CCD3E0>\n\n< ! > Utilisez votre Couteau de Combat contre les ennemis plus faibles pour \u00e9conomiser les munitions.\n\n< ! > Obtenir l'\u00c9chantillon de G-Virus vous donnera une carte-cl\u00e9, permettant d'acc\u00e9der aux mallettes d'armes \u00e0 chaque \u00c9tape.\n\n< ! > Utilisez Quickstep pr\u00e8s d'un ennemi ou d'un projectile attaquant pour effectuer une Esquive Parfaite, puis contre-attaquez avec votre Primaire.\n\n< ! > Les munitions sont rares, mais peuvent \u00eatre trouv\u00e9es dans les coffres ouverts. Les stocks secondaires et la r\u00e9duction de recharge affectent \u00e9galement les munitions.\n\n< ! > C'est la guerre. La survie est votre responsabilit\u00e9. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SUBTITLE": "Le Faucheur",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "..et ainsi il partit, tout va bien.",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_OUTRO_FAILURE": "..et ainsi il disparut, unit\u00e9 humaine maintenant neutralis\u00e9e.",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_DEFAULT_SKIN_NAME": "Par d\u00e9faut",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_CLASSIC_SKIN_NAME": "RE2make",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_TOFU_SKIN_NAME": "Tofu",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SUPER_SKIN_NAME": "<color=#FFFF00>Early Supporter</color>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_LIGHTWEIGHT_SKIN_NAME": "L\u00e9ger",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_GUERRILLA_SKIN_NAME": "Troupier",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_ROOKIE_SKIN_NAME": "Recrue",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SWAT_SKIN_NAME": "Pacificateur",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_LEON_SKIN_NAME": "Specialist",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_LEONSHIRT_SKIN_NAME": "Specialist EX",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_ENFORCER_SKIN_NAME": "Bulldozer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_WESKER_SKIN_NAME": "Mastermind",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_DOOM_SKIN_NAME": "Slayer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_COMMANDO_SKIN_NAME": "Commando",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_JACKET_SKIN_NAME": "Veste",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PPASSIVE_NAME": "OSP (On-Site Procurement)",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PPASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "HUNK peut collecter des <color=#FFFF00>U.C. Keycards</color> pour ouvrir des <style=cIsDamage>mallettes d'armes</style> et \u00e9tendre son arsenal. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PPASSIVE2_NAME": "Soldat Oubli\u00e9",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PPASSIVE2_DESCRIPTION": "Le premier <style=cIsHealth>boss</style> \u00e0 mourir \u00e0 chaque \u00c9tape laisse tomber un <style=cIsDamage>paquet de ravitaillement</style> contenant une arme ou un accessoire. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PASSIVE_NAME": "Combat Obscur",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "Commencez avec une <style=cIsDamage>LE 5</style> et une <style=cIsDamage>arme secondaire</style>. Vous pouvez <style=cIsDamage>fouiller</style> <style=cIsUtility>les coffres</style> pour trouver des munitions. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PASSIVE2_NAME": "Effroi Imminent",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PASSIVE2_DESCRIPTION": "Commencez avec un <style=cIsDamage>arsenal complet</style>, <style=cIsHealth>MAIS</style> vous ne pouvez plus <style=cIsHealth>obtenir de munitions suppl\u00e9mentaires</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_RANDOMPASSIVE_NAME": "New Game+",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_RANDOMPASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "Commencez avec une <style=cIsDamage>LE 5</style> et une <style=cIsDamage>arme secondaire</style>. Vous pouvez <style=cIsDamage>fouiller</style> <style=cIsUtility>les coffres</style> pour trouver des munitions. <style=cIsHealth>Tout le contenu des mallettes d'armes est al\u00e9atoire.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOTGUNPASSIVE_NAME": "Autorit\u00e9 Supr\u00eame",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOTGUNPASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "Commencez avec une <style=cIsDamage>W-870</style> et une <style=cIsDamage>arme secondaire</style>. Vous pouvez <style=cIsDamage>fouiller</style> <style=cIsUtility>les coffres</style> pour trouver des munitions. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SMGPASSIVE_NAME": "Mercenaire Supr\u00eame",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SMGPASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "Commencez <style=cIsHealth>SEULEMENT</style> avec une <style=cIsDamage>LE 5 enti\u00e8rement am\u00e9lior\u00e9e</style>. Vous pouvez <style=cIsDamage>fouiller</style> <style=cIsUtility>les coffres</style> pour trouver des munitions. La <style=cIsDamage>Sp\u00e9ciale</style> est remplac\u00e9e par <color=#C80202>Mode Chaos</color>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_WPASSIVE_NAME": "Saturation Globale Compl\u00e8te",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_WPASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "Commencez <style=cIsHealth>SEULEMENT</style> avec une <style=cIsDamage>arme secondaire</style>. Vous pouvez <style=cIsDamage>fouiller</style> <style=cIsUtility>les coffres</style> pour trouver des munitions. L'<style=cIsDamage>Utilitaire</style> est remplac\u00e9 par <color=#C80202>Uroboros</color>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_FLAMERPASSIVE_NAME": "Pyromanie",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_FLAMERPASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "Commencez <style=cIsHealth>SEULEMENT</style> avec un <style=cIsDamage>Lance-flammes Chimique</style>. Vous pouvez <style=cIsDamage>fouiller</style> <style=cIsUtility>les coffres</style> pour trouver des munitions. <style=cIsHealth>Seulement UNE mallette d'armes appara\u00eet par \u00c9tape.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PRIMARY_KNIFE_NAME": "Couteau de Combat",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PRIMARY_KNIFE_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Tirez.</style> <style=cIsDamage>Tranchez</style> les combattants proches pour <style=cIsDamage>200% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>, infligeant <style=cIsHealth>Mutil\u00e9</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PRIMARY_CQC_NAME": "CQC (Combat de Proximit\u00e9)",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PRIMARY_CQC_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Tirez.</style> <style=cIsDamage>Donnez deux coups de pied</style> pour <style=cIsDamage>200% et 250% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. Si le <style=cIsUtility>deuxi\u00e8me coup de pied</style> touche, encha\u00eenez avec une <style=cIsDamage>Contre-attaque</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_PRIMARY_RELOAD_NAME": "Recharger",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_RELOAD_DESCRIPTION": "Rechargez votre arme actuelle. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SECONDARY_AIM_NAME": "Viser Ferme",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SECONDARY_AIM_DESCRIPTION": "Visez, <style=cIsUtility>exposant les points faibles ennemis</style>. <style=cIsDamage>Utiliser le primaire en visant tire votre arme \u00e9quip\u00e9e.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_DODGE_NAME": "Quickstep",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_DODGE_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Avancez</style> d'une courte distance. Si utilis\u00e9 de mani\u00e8re pr\u00e9ventive pour <style=cIsUtility>\u00e9viter une attaque</style>, effectuez une <style=cIsDamage>Esquive Parfaite</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_DODGE_SCEPTER_NAME": "Uroboros",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_DODGE_SCEPTER_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Avancez</style> d'une courte distance. Si utilis\u00e9 de mani\u00e8re pr\u00e9ventive pour <style=cIsUtility>\u00e9viter une attaque</style>, effectuez une <style=cIsDamage>Esquive Parfaite</style>. Le pouvoir d'Uroboros coule en vous. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_PARRY_NAME": "Parade",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_PARRY_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Bloquez</style> une attaque, <style=cIsDamage>annulant</style> les d\u00e9g\u00e2ts et <style=cIsUtility>remboursant le temps de recharge</style>. Si utilis\u00e9 de mani\u00e8re pr\u00e9ventive, effectuez une <style=cIsDamage>Parade Parfaite</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_BASH_NAME": "Coup d'\u00e9paule",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_UTILITY_BASH_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Frappez</style> les ennemis proches avec l'\u00e9paule, <style=cIsUtility>les \u00e9tourdissant</style> pour <style=cIsDamage>400% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. Si utilis\u00e9 de mani\u00e8re pr\u00e9ventive pour <style=cIsUtility>annuler une attaque</style>, effectuez une <style=cIsDamage>D\u00e9flexion Parfaite</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SPECIAL_SWAP_NAME": "L\u00e9gion",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SPECIAL_SWAP_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>\u00c9changez</style> pour une <style=cIsDamage>arme diff\u00e9rente</style>. Appuyez pour \u00e9changer vers <style=cIsUtility>votre derni\u00e8re arme utilis\u00e9e</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SPECIAL_MAYHEM_NAME": "Mode Chaos",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SPECIAL_MAYHEM_DESCRIPTION": "Entrez en <style=cIsDamage>Mode Chaos</style>, augmentant consid\u00e9rablement les performances de l'arme. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_CONFIRM_NAME": "Confirmer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_CONFIRM_DESCRIPTION": "Proc\u00e9der avec la comp\u00e9tence actuelle. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_CANCEL_NAME": "Annuler",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_CANCEL_DESCRIPTION": "Annuler la comp\u00e9tence actuelle. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_DEFAULT_NAME": "Couteau de Combat",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_DEFAULT_DESCRIPTION": "Un couteau militaire standard. Certainement utile dans les moments difficiles. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_INFINITE_NAME": "Couteau de Combat EX",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_INFINITE_DESCRIPTION": "Un couteau militaire trait\u00e9 sp\u00e9cialement qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 durci \u00e0 un degr\u00e9 incroyable. On dit qu'il est fait pour durer vraiment. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_HIDDEN_NAME": "Lame Cach\u00e9e",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_HIDDEN_DESCRIPTION": "Une lame r\u00e9tractable discr\u00e8te cach\u00e9e dans la manche. Id\u00e9ale pour les op\u00e9rations furtives. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_WESKER_NAME": "Couteau Personnalis\u00e9",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_WESKER_DESCRIPTION": "Une lame cruelle au bord dentel\u00e9 pour aider \u00e0 lac\u00e9rer vos adversaires. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_MACHETE_NAME": "Machette",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_MACHETE_DESCRIPTION": "Une lame \u00e9norme principalement destin\u00e9e aux tactiques de gu\u00e9rilla. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_RE4_NAME": "Couteau Principal",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_RE4_DESCRIPTION": "Un couteau forg\u00e9 avec des possibilit\u00e9s infinies. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_BLOODY_NAME": "Lame Ensanglant\u00e9e",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_BLOODY_DESCRIPTION": "Une lame ensanglant\u00e9e au bord dentel\u00e9 qui a d\u00e9j\u00e0 lac\u00e9r\u00e9 de nombreux adversaires. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_HOTDOGGER_NAME": "HOT DOGGER",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_HOTDOGGER_DESCRIPTION": "Comme le nom l'indique, ce couteau anti-bioweapon d\u00e9velopp\u00e9 par Umbrella est utilis\u00e9 par ceux qui aiment se mettre en valeur. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_STUNROD_NAME": "B"};
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_STUNROD_DESCRIPTION": "AVERTISSEMENT : N'\u00e9tourdir pas vraiment. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_KITCHEN_NAME": "Couteau de Cuisine",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_KNIFE_KITCHEN_DESCRIPTION": "Un couteau fait pour cuisiner. Sa lame s'\u00e9caille facilement. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SMG_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SMG_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>110% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>25% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_M19_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_M19_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>500% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>100% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SG09_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SG09_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>500% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>50% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_BROOMHC_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_BROOMHC_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>180% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>25% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MAGNUM_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MAGNUM_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>1.200% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>50% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_GOLDGUN_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_GOLDGUN_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>99.999% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>50% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MUP_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MUP_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>320% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>25% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_REVOLVER_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_REVOLVER_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>1.200% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>50% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_COLT_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_COLT_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>2.000% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>50% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SPARKSHOT_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SPARKSHOT_DESCRIPTION": "Tire une aiguille \u00e9lectrifi\u00e9e pour <style=cIsDamage>1.000% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Rebondit jusqu'\u00e0 3 ennemis pour <style=cIsDamage>2.000% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_BLUEROSE_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_BLUEROSE_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>2x3.800% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>50% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SHOTGUN_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SHOTGUN_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>14x150% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>50% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_M3_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_M3_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>10x130% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>50% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SSG_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SSG_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>16x200% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>50% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_STREETSWEEPER_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_STREETSWEEPER_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>14x24% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>25% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SLUGGER_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SLUGGER_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>3.000% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>50% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_AR_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_AR_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>385% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>50% de bonus en tir \u00e0 la t\u00eate.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MINIGUN_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MINIGUN_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>2x250% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Les d\u00e9g\u00e2ts augmentent avec la vitesse d'attaque.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_ATM_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_ATM_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>8.000% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Inflige plus de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts sur les coups directs.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_ATM2_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_ATM2_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>8.000% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Inflige plus de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts sur les coups directs.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_RPG_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_RPG_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>8.000% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Inflige plus de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts sur les coups directs.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_ROCKETLAUNCHER_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_ROCKETLAUNCHER_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>12.000% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsDamage>Incendiaire.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_GRENADELAUNCHER_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_GRENADELAUNCHER_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>3.200% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsDamage>Incendiaire.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MGL_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_MGL_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>2.400% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_RAILGUN_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_RAILGUN_DESCRIPTION": "Tire pour <style=cIsDamage>20.000% de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_FLAMETHROWER_NAME": "Tirer",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_FLAMETHROWER_DESCRIPTION": "Tire un jet de flammes pour <style=cIsDamage>des tonnes de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Enflamme.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SCANNER_NAME": "Scanner",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_SCANNER_DESCRIPTION": "Scanne pour <style=cIsUtility>les mallettes d'armes non ouvertes</style>. <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_HOOKSHOT_NAME": "Grappin",
        "ROB_HUNK_BODY_SHOOT_HOOKSHOT_DESCRIPTION": "Tirez un grappin vers un <style=cIsUtility>point \u00e9loign\u00e9</style>, puis <style=cIsUtility>tirez-vous vers lui</style>. <style=cIsDamage>Vous pouvez contre-attaquer apr\u00e8s l'atterrissage.</style> <i>Translated by: Jaosnake. Original mod by rob</i>",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYWORD_MANGLED": "Mutil\u00e9",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYWORD_COUNTER": "Contre-attaque",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYWORD_PERFECTDODGE": "Esquive Parfaite",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYWORD_PERFECTBASH": "D\u00e9flexion Parfaite",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYWORD_PERFECTPARRY": "Parade Parfaite",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYWORD_CVIRUS": "C-Virus",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYWORD_GVIRUS": "G-Virus",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYWORD_TVIRUS": "T-Virus",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYWORD_VIRUS": "Virus",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYWORD_LOOTING": "Pillage",
        "ROB_HUNK_JETPACK_NAME": "Pack de Saut Exp\u00e9rimental",
        "ROB_HUNK_JETPACK_DESC": "Un outil fabriqu\u00e9 par Umbrella qui vous permet de vous propulser dans n'importe quelle direction en appuyant sur saut dans les airs.",
        "ROB_HUNK_SURVIVALKIT_NAME": "Kit de Survie d'Urgence",
        "ROB_HUNK_SURVIVALKIT_DESC": "Un kit de survie qui augmente \u00e0 la fois votre capacit\u00e9 \u00e0 fouiller pour des munitions et l'efficacit\u00e9 de votre couteau.",
        "ROB_HUNK_TRANSCEIVER_NAME": "\u00c9metteur-r\u00e9cepteur Us\u00e9",
        "ROB_HUNK_TRANSCEIVER_DESC": "Appelle un co\u00e9quipier pour aider dans votre op\u00e9ration.",
        "ROB_HUNK_INFROCKET_NAME": "ATM-4",
        "ROB_HUNK_INFROCKET_DESC": "Un lance-roquettes avec <style=cIsHealing>des munitions infinies</style>. R\u00e9compense pour le succ\u00e8s <color=#FFFF00>Early Supporter</color>.",
        "ROB_HUNK_TYPEWRITER_NAME": "Machine \u00e0 \u00c9crire",
        "ROB_HUNK_TYPEWRITER_DESC": "Accorde <style=cIsUtility>2</style> <color=#C80202>mallettes d'armes Umbrella</color> suppl\u00e9mentaires par \u00c9tape.",
        "ROB_HUNK_CRYSTALSKULL_NAME": "Cr\u00e2ne de Cristal",
        "ROB_HUNK_CRYSTALSKULL_DESC": "Un tr\u00e9sor rare. Peut \u00eatre \u00e9chang\u00e9 dans n'importe quel <style=cIsUtility>Chaudron</style> pour recevoir un objet.",
        "ROB_HUNK_WRISTBAND_NAME": "Bracelet d'Identification",
        "ROB_HUNK_WRISTBAND_DESC": "Une cl\u00e9 \u00e9lectronique pour utilisation dans les installations de <color=#C80202>Umbrella Corporation</color>. Utilis\u00e9e pour ouvrir une <style=cIsUtility>mallette d'arme sp\u00e9ciale</style>.",
        "ROB_HUNK_SPADE_KEYCARD_NAME": "U.C. Keycard (Piques)",
        "ROB_HUNK_CLUB_KEYCARD_NAME": "U.C. Keycard (Tr\u00e8fles)",
        "ROB_HUNK_HEART_KEYCARD_NAME": "U.C. Keycard (C\u0153urs)",
        "ROB_HUNK_DIAMOND_KEYCARD_NAME": "U.C. Keycard (Carreaux)",
        "ROB_HUNK_GOLD_KEYCARD_NAME": "U.C. Keycard (\u00c9toile)",
        "ROB_HUNK_MASTER_KEYCARD_NAME": "U.C. Keycard (Ma\u00eetre)",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYCARD_DESC": "Utilis\u00e9 pour ouvrir les <color=#C80202>mallettes d'armes</color> de <style=cIsUtility>Umbrella Corporation</style>.",
        "ROB_HUNK_KEYCARD_MASTER_DESC": "Utilis\u00e9 pour ouvrir les <color=#C80202>mallettes d'armes</color> de <style=cIsUtility>Umbrella Corporation</style>. Ouvre <style=cIsHealing>toutes les mallettes</style> et transforme les autres keycards en <style=cIsUtility>ferraille</style>.",
        "ROB_HUNK_STARSBADGE_NAME": "Badge S.T.A.R.S.",
        "ROB_HUNK_STARSBADGE_DESC": "Un badge sp\u00e9cial de la division des forces sp\u00e9ciales du R.P.D., <color=#F20443>S.T.A.R.S.</color> <style=cIsHealth>Peut-\u00eatre que prendre cela \u00e9tait une mauvaise id\u00e9e?</style>",
        "ROB_HUNK_STARSBADGE_DESCFULL": "Chaque \u00c9tape, une mallette sp\u00e9ciale <color=#F20443>S.T.A.R.S.</color> appara\u00eet qui ne peut \u00eatre ouverte qu'avec ce badge. Cependant, le <style=cIsHealth>Nemesis T-Type</style> vous traquera impitoyablement.",
        "ROB_HUNK_STARSBADGE2_NAME": "Cl\u00e9 USB Dongle",
        "ROB_HUNK_STARSBADGE2_DESC": "Utilis\u00e9e pour acc\u00e9der \u00e0 un <style=cIsUtility>coffre sp\u00e9cial</style> \u00e0 chaque \u00c9tape.",
        "ROB_HUNK_STARSBADGE2_DESCFULL": "Chaque \u00c9tape, une mallette sp\u00e9ciale <color=#F20443>S.T.A.R.S.</color> appara\u00eet qui ne peut \u00eatre ouverte qu'avec ce badge. Cependant, le <style=cIsHealth>Nemesis T-Type</style> vous traquera impitoyablement.",
        "ROB_HUNK_HEARTCHEST_NAME": "Coffre du C\u0153ur",
        "ROB_HUNK_NEMICASE_NAME": "Cas Nemi",
        "ROB_HUNK_NEMICASE_DESC": "Un cas myst\u00e9rieux.",
        "ROB_HUNK_AMMO_NAME": "Munitions",
        "ROB_HUNK_AMMOITEM_NAME": "Munitions",
        "ROB_HUNK_CHEST_NAME": "Coffre",
